# A [[widespread]] [[disease]] that [[affect]]s many [[individual]]s in a [[population]].
# {{context|epidemiology|lang=en}} An [[occurrence]] of a disease or [[disorder]] in a population at a [[frequency]] higher than that expected in a given time period.

